Enum SHNDataType

  • java.lang.Object
    • java.lang.Enum<SHNDataType>
      • com.philips.pins.shinelib.datatypes.SHNDataType
  • All Implemented Interfaces:
    Serializable, Comparable<SHNDataType>

    public enum SHNDataType
extends Enum<SHNDataType>
    All datatypes supported by BlueLib.

    Returned by classes inheriting SHNData.getSHNDataType() to indicate what datatype they are.
